<rss version="2.0" xmlns:atom="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom"><channel><title>some.pics (中文)</title><link>https://some.pics</link><description>只是网上的一些图片。</description><language>zh-CN</language><lastBuildDate>Sat, 18 Apr 2026 08:59:26 +0000</lastBuildDate><item><title>Oakley Why 3 金色无框太阳镜</title><link>https://some.pics/69e347e828353</link><description>&lt;p&gt;一副太阳镜（Oakley Why 3款），配有处方镜片，镜片呈深绿色调，镜框为无框金色，采用运动有机设计，线条略带尖角，平放在一张黄灰色桌子上。眼镜的一条镜腿笔直伸展，另一条则在镜片后方呈一定角度。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;img alt="A pair of sunglasses (Oakley Why 3) with prescription lenses with a dark green tint and a rimless golden in sporting organic, slightly pointy lines laying on a yellowish grey table. One arm of the glasses is extended straight, the other is angled behind the lenses. " height="1797" referrerpolicy="no-referrer" src="https://cdn.some.pics/mangochutney/69e347e828353.jpg" width="2696"/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Shared by &lt;a href="https://mangochutney.some.pics"&gt;@mangochutney&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Sat, 18 Apr 2026 08:59:26 +0000</pubDate></item><item><title>暖光下的惊愕猫咪</title><link>https://some.pics/69e2ebc88970a</link><description>&lt;p&gt;温暖灯光下的托蒂科猫，略带惊讶地直视着我们。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;img alt="Warmly-lit tortico cat looking a little startled directly at us." height="2666" referrerpolicy="no-referrer" src="https://cdn.some.pics/hp/69e2ebc88970a.jpg" width="4000"/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Shared by &lt;a href="https://hp.some.pics"&gt;@hp&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Sat, 18 Apr 2026 02:26:23 +0000</pubDate></item><item><title>被扰清梦的猫</title><link>https://some.pics/69e2eb9c029b4</link><description>&lt;p&gt;托蒂科猫沐浴在温暖的光线中，看起来因为美梦被打扰而面露不悦。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;img alt="Tortico cat bathed in warm light looking annoyed that her slumber was disturbed." height="2666" referrerpolicy="no-referrer" src="https://cdn.some.pics/hp/69e2eb9c029b4.jpg" width="4000"/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Shared by &lt;a href="https://hp.some.pics"&gt;@hp&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Sat, 18 Apr 2026 02:25:37 +0000</pubDate></item><item><title>郁金香盛开</title><link>https://some.pics/69e2e2531d2a7</link><description>&lt;p&gt;郁金香，郁金香，郁金香！&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;img alt="Tulips, tulips, tulips! " height="4032" referrerpolicy="no-referrer" src="https://cdn.some.pics/rrajath/69e2e2531d2a7.jpg" width="2268"/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Shared by &lt;a href="https://rrajath.some.pics"&gt;@rrajath&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Sat, 18 Apr 2026 01:45:57 +0000</pubDate></item><item><title>非洲菊特写</title><link>https://some.pics/69e2c676df166</link><description>&lt;p&gt;一些非洲菊的美丽特写。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;img alt="A cluster of white and pale purple African daisies with dark purple centers, set in green foliage over wood mulch." height="3000" referrerpolicy="no-referrer" src="https://cdn.some.pics/sjwallin/69e2c676df166.jpg" width="1905"/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Shared by &lt;a href="https://sjwallin.some.pics"&gt;@sjwallin&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Fri, 17 Apr 2026 23:47:05 +0000</pubDate></item></channel></rss>